How to create Provider.

1)Add dependency in pubsec.yaml file.
2)Create a class that has business logic use 'with' for changeNotifier.
3)Use 'notifylistner' where the business logic is implemented in the provider class.


Disdavatage
***********
Consumer:- Without Consumer implementation the entire widget will rebuild in Provider.

This disadvantage is avoided with the implementation of the consumer.
With the implementation of Consumer,only the required widget will ReBuild.